Argentine Official Says Researchers’ CPI Reports Are Unreliable

-- B y   E l i a n a   R a s z e w s k i
-- 
2011-09-26T20:29:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/argentine-official-says-researchers-cpi-reports-are-unreliable.html
Reports prepared by Argentine
researchers that indicate inflation is running at a faster rate
than that reported by the government are unreliable, Ana Maria
Edwin, director of  Argentina ’s national statistics agency, said
at a press conference today in  Buenos Aires .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eliana Raszewski in Buenos Aires at 
 eraszewski@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Richard Jarvie at 
